divs: Sighting Detailsa freind of mine and i were leaving lake travis when this object rose above the tree line.as if it seen us lowerd below the tree line.broad daylight,it was gone as fast as it appeared.there were cows being killed with vital organs missing at the time.reason this is being brought up now is why would any "space ship" have lights on it and why would they coinside with airplane landing lights.
